00:14:23,213 --> 00:14:26,713
やっほー！ぼこぼこーこぼ・かなえる、アットユアサービス！
Hi! Boko boko Kobo Kanaeru, at your service!

161
00:14:26,713 --> 00:14:30,213
Let me be your sun to shine your day! Ehe!

162
00:14:26,713 --> 00:14:30,213
君の日々を照らす太陽になりましょう！えへ！
Let me be the sun that lights up your days! Ehe!

163
00:14:30,213 --> 00:14:33,713
Kobokers, mana suaranya!
Kobokers, let me hear you!

164
00:14:30,213 --> 00:14:33,713
Kobokers声を上げて！
Kobokers, raise your voices!

165
00:14:38,213 --> 00:14:40,713
3人で...
Together...

166
00:14:41,213 --> 00:14:47,713
hololive Indonesia Gen 3, Holoh3ro!

167
00:14:41,213 --> 00:14:47,713
ホロライブインドネシア3期生、holoh3roでーす！
We are hololive Indonesia Gen 3, Holoh3ro!

168
00:14:52,713 --> 00:14:59,213
Wah nggak nyangka juga deh konser 5th anniversary hololive ID ini akhirnya ada juga.
Wow, I didn't expect that the hololive ID 5th anniversary concert would finally happen.

169
00:14:52,713 --> 00:14:59,213
やあ、ついにホロライブID 5周年ライブができるとはね。
Man, I can't believe we can finally have a hololive ID 5th anniversary live.

170
00:14:59,213 --> 00:15:03,713
Dari lagu pertama aja udah keren banget guys. Kerasa gak sih semangatnya?
Even from the first song it's already so cool guys. Can you feel the energy?

171
00:14:59,213 --> 00:15:03,713
一曲目からもうめっちゃカッコいいよね！その熱気、感じてるわ！わ！
Even from the first song it's already super cool! I'm feeling that heat! Yeah!

172
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:05,472
Enggak sih, iya enggak sih, iya enggak sih?
Maybe not, or is it, or is it?

173
00:15:05,472 --> 00:15:06,472
Parah sih!
It's intense!

174
00:15:06,472 --> 00:15:09,272
Adrenalinnya keluar kan ya? Pengen lari aku rasanya nih!
Adrenaline is flowing, right? I feel like running!

175
00:15:09,272 --> 00:15:12,672
Eh eh eh! Mau ke mana? Mau ke mana?
Hey hey hey! Where are you going? Where are you going?

176
00:15:14,972 --> 00:15:18,072
Iya iya sst, ya udah stop stop stop stop stop stop stop!
Yes yes, okay stop stop stop stop stop stop stop!

177
00:15:18,072 --> 00:15:20,972
Nanti keringetan loh, nanti keringetan!
You'll get sweaty, you'll get sweaty!

178
00:15:21,472 --> 00:15:22,672
Ah, kalau Kaela gimana?
Ah, what about Kaela?

179
00:15:22,672 --> 00:15:27,672
Aduh, seru banget! Aku enggak nyangka sih sampai aku bisa ada di sini ya.
Man, it's so fun! I didn't expect to be able to be here.

180
00:15:28,172 --> 00:15:32,672
Tapi ini ngomong-ngomong, konsernya masih panjang banget, jadi kalian tetap semangat ya sampai akhir!
But by the way, this concert is still very long, so keep your spirits up until the end!

181
00:15:33,172 --> 00:15:37,172
Sampai akhir! Semangat semangat semangat semangat!
Until the end! Go go go go!

182
00:15:37,672 --> 00:15:42,372
Eh tapi ngomongin konser dari tadi, emang pada tahu judul konsernya apa?
Eh, but talking about the concert all this time, does everyone know the title of the concert?

183
00:15:43,172 --> 00:15:47,172
Judul konser kita kali ini adalah "Chromatic Future"!
The title of our concert this time is "Chromatic Future"!

184
00:15:48,172 --> 00:15:50,172
Ada yang tahu enggak artinya apa? Ayo absen!
Does anyone know what it means? Come on, check in!

185
00:15:51,172 --> 00:15:53,172
Nah ini, Kobo paling tahu!
Now this, Kobo knows best!

186
00:15:54,172 --> 00:15:59,672
Nih, ah... yang jelasin yang paling tinggi. Yuk let's go!
Here, ah... the tallest one explains. Come on, let's go!

187
00:16:01,172 --> 00:16:02,672
Segitu ya? Ya udahlah, ya udah.
Is that so? Oh well, okay.

188
00:16:03,172 --> 00:16:08,672
Nih ya guys ya buat kalian yang belum tahu, "Chromatic Future" itu artinya tuh masa depan yang berwarna-warni.
So guys, for those who don't know, "Chromatic Future" means a colorful future.

189
00:16:09,172 --> 00:16:15,172
Jadi karena Hololive Indonesia kan sudah 5 tahun nih, kita sama-sama dari hari satu sampai sekarang.
So because Hololive Indonesia has been around for 5 years now, we've been together from day one until now.

190
00:16:16,172 --> 00:16:19,672
Nah, jadi itu untuk ke depannya kita tuh juga
So, for the future, our hope is that we can

191
00:16:19,672 --> 00:16:23,172
harapannya tuh kita bisa nyiptain waktu dan memori
create colorful times and memories

192
00:16:23,172 --> 00:16:26,672
yang berwarna-warni sama seluruh fans dari Hololive Indonesia!
with all the fans of Hololive Indonesia!

193
00:16:27,172 --> 00:16:32,672
Ya gitu! Betul Kaela Kovalskia! Catat catat! Iya iya iya iya!
That's right! Correct Kaela Kovalskia! Note it down! Yes yes yes!

194
00:16:34,672 --> 00:16:38,672
Nah, kalian sekarang udah pada tahu kan? Karena tadi udah dijelasin sama Kaela.
Now, you all know now, right? Because Kaela already explained it.

195
00:16:39,172 --> 00:16:41,672
Kalau gitu, konsernya kan udah mulai nih.
In that case, the concert has already started.

196
00:16:42,172 --> 00:16:50,672
Kalian mau nge-post soal konser ini di medsos, jangan lupa hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture ya!
If you want to post about this concert on social media, don't forget the hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture!

197
00:16:51,172 --> 00:16:55,172
Karena kita pengen banget lihat kalian tuh...
Because we really want to see your...

198
00:16:55,172 --> 00:16:59,172
apa sih? Pengen lihat semangat kalian!
what is it? We want to see your spirit!

199
00:17:00,172 --> 00:17:03,172
Ya itu! Betul banget, iya enggak?
Yeah, that! Absolutely right, isn't it?

200
00:17:04,172 --> 00:17:05,672
Jangan typo, jangan typo!
No typos, no typos!

201
00:17:06,172 --> 00:17:08,672
Asyik, share ke semua! Oke!
Cool, share to everyone! Okay!

202
00:17:09,172 --> 00:17:15,172
Jadi tapi jujur deh, kalian tuh pas dibilang kita bakal konser loh di Indonesia, kalian pada kaget enggak sih?
So, but be honest, when you were told we were going to have a concert in Indonesia, were you surprised?

203
00:17:16,172 --> 00:17:18,172
Halo? Ada yang dengerin?
Hello? Is anyone listening?

204
00:17:18,672 --> 00:17:24,172
Betul! Aku setuju juga, aku merasakan empati...
Correct! I agree too, I feel empathy...

205
00:17:25,172 --> 00:17:29,672
...terhadap adik saya Zeta. / Empati iya iya.
...towards my sister Zeta. / Empathy, yes yes.

206
00:17:30,172 --> 00:17:31,672
Kalau Kaela gimana, Kaela Kovalskia?
How about Kaela, Kaela Kovalskia?

207
00:17:31,672 --> 00:17:35,672
Aku juga waktu itu enggak nyangka banget kayak "Hah? Beneran? Ini riil nih?" gitu kan.
I also didn't expect it at the time, like "Huh? Really? Is this real?"

208
00:17:36,172 --> 00:17:42,672
Kayak "Lho, bisa gitu? Akhirnya!" Mana udah bersembilan di Indonesia pula, ya kan? Keren banget!
Like "Wait, how? Finally!" Especially since all nine of us are in Indonesia, right? So cool!

209
00:17:45,172 --> 00:17:46,672
Keren banget!
So cool!

210
00:17:47,172 --> 00:17:50,672
Ini kan konser pertama Hololive Indonesia yang bersembilan.
This is the first Hololive Indonesia concert with all nine members.

211
00:17:51,172 --> 00:17:54,172
Sebenarnya tuh enggak hanya ini tuh momen terbesar
Actually, this is not only the biggest and

212
00:17:54,172 --> 00:17:57,172
dan terpenting juga untuk fans Hololive Indonesia,
most important moment for Hololive Indonesia fans,

213
00:17:57,172 --> 00:18:00,672
tapi seluruh dunia juga pasti bakal nonton,
but the whole world will surely be watching,

214
00:18:00,672 --> 00:18:03,672
enggak sih? Iya enggak?
right? Isn't it?

215
00:18:04,172 --> 00:18:07,672
Jawab!
Answer!

216
00:18:08,172 --> 00:18:15,672
Iya iya makasih makasih semuanya. Tapi tentu aja ini pencapaiannya enggak bakal cuma sampai di sini aja kan?
Yes, yes, thank you everyone. But of course this achievement won't just stop here, right?

217
00:18:16,172 --> 00:18:21,672
Jadi next-nya mungkin kita bisa apa ya? Dominating the world! Gitu! We are ready!
So next, maybe we can... what? Dominate the world! Like that! We are ready!

218
00:18:22,172 --> 00:18:26,672
Ready ready ready ready! Betul banget Kaela! Zeta!
Ready ready ready ready! That's right, Kaela! Zeta!

219
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:30,672
Selain dari dukungan fans in this opportunity...
Besides the support of the fans in this opportunity...

220
00:18:30,672 --> 00:18:33,672
...kita juga mau mengucapkan terima kasih
...we also want to say thank you to all the

221
00:18:33,672 --> 00:18:35,672
untuk semua sponsor yang mendukung terjadinya konser ini!
sponsors who supported this concert!

222
00:18:36,172 --> 00:18:43,672
Terima kasih! Makasih makasih! Thank you thank you!
Thank you! Thanks thanks! Thank you thank you!

223
00:18:44,172 --> 00:18:48,172
Eh tapi ngomong-ngomong di konser ini
Eh, but by the way, in this concert

224
00:18:48,172 --> 00:18:52,672
kayaknya ada yang beda enggak sih? Ela kamu nyadar enggak?
there seems to be something different, isn't there? Ela, did you notice?

225
00:18:52,672 --> 00:18:56,672
Sadar lah! Kalau Kobo mah enggak bakal sadar.
Of course! Kobo wouldn't notice.

226
00:18:57,172 --> 00:19:04,672
Nih nih nih, yang beda tuh kali ini tuh model kita! Ini model baru nih!
Here here here, what's different this time is our models! These are new models!

227
00:19:05,172 --> 00:19:12,672
Gemes banget! Lucu lucu lucu!
So cute! Cute cute cute!

228
00:19:13,172 --> 00:19:17,672
Kameranya deketin ke aku! Kameranya deketin ke aku!
Bring the camera closer to me! Bring the camera closer to me!

229
00:19:18,172 --> 00:19:21,672
Nah mulai mulai. Kalian mau lihat keimutan Kobo nih nih...
Here we go. You want to see Kobo's cuteness...

230
00:19:22,172 --> 00:19:24,672
Ini ini, osiri!
This one, my butt!

231
00:19:25,172 --> 00:19:32,172
Woi woi woi! Kameranya diambil Kobo semua enggak sih?
Hey hey hey! The camera is all taken by Kobo, right?

232
00:19:32,172 --> 00:19:39,672
Ini ke aku! Aku juga! Jangan Kobo doang!
To me! Me too! Not just Kobo!

233
00:19:40,172 --> 00:19:46,672
Stop stop stop stop! Mulai mulai mulai... Semua kamera diambil!
Stop stop stop stop! Here we go... All the cameras are taken!

234
00:19:47,172 --> 00:19:52,172
Oke oke. Kalau gitu... aduh sampai kehabisan napas.
Okay okay. In that case... man, I'm out of breath.

235
00:19:52,172 --> 00:19:56,672
Jangan rebutan di depan konser!
Don't fight in front of the concert!

236
00:19:57,172 --> 00:20:00,672
Iya iya.
Yes yes.

237
00:20:01,172 --> 00:20:04,172
Hati-hati ya, Zeta kalau marah tuh serem loh.
Be careful, Zeta is scary when she's angry.

238
00:20:04,141 --> 00:20:05,700
はいよ、ゼータが怒ると怖いからね
Yeah, it's scary when Zeta gets angry.

239
00:20:05,772 --> 00:20:07,272
怖いよー
I'm scared...

240
00:20:07,361 --> 00:20:13,248
もういいや、ゼータがカメラも独り占めしちゃダメっていうのは…うーん、しょうがない
Fine, whatever. If Zeta says we can't hog the camera, then... sigh, it can't be helped.

241
00:20:13,339 --> 00:20:16,941
ファンの皆んなと遊ぼう！
Let's just play with the fans instead!

242
00:20:17,028 --> 00:20:20,701
さっきみんなからも大きな声もらったわけだし今度はこっちがみんなに大きな声を出したいっす！
Since everyone cheered for us earlier, this time I want us to cheer for you all!

243
00:20:20,837 --> 00:20:24,870
はいはいはい、みんなと一緒に大きな声を出したいっすね！
Yes, yes, yes. I want us to shout our cheers together with the fans!

244
00:20:25,328 --> 00:20:29,248
そう！みんなにじゃなく、みんなとね
Exactly! Shout with them, not at them.

245
00:20:29,383 --> 00:20:30,801
そうそう！そういうことっす！
Yeah! That's what I meant!

246
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:35,690
だってこれから歌わなきゃいけないからまずは声を温存しなきゃでしょ？
We have to sing later, so shouldn't we save our voices first?

247
00:20:35,837 --> 00:20:42,701
そうっすよ、そんなにカエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's true. It won't take as long as one of my streams, so don't worry, guys.

248
00:20:42,939 --> 00:20:46,870
まあいい、大声出していいから好きにして
Fine, if you want to shout, go ahead. I'm in.

249
00:20:46,941 --> 00:20:49,690
みんな準備はいいかな？
How about it, everyone? Are you ready?

250
00:20:49,837 --> 00:20:52,248
いけるかな？
Ready or not?!

251
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:57,701
もう出来てるのかよっすね！じゃあここから！
Seems like they are! Okay, starting with Kobo!

252
00:20:57,772 --> 00:21:02,801
一緒に「BOKOBOKOBO！」って叫ぼう！よろしくいこうよ！
I want us all to shout "BOKOBOKOBO!" together. Okay?

253
00:21:03,939 --> 00:21:07,941
いち、に、さん！
Ready? One, two, three!

254
00:21:08,028 --> 00:21:11,272
BOKOBOKOBO！
BOKOBOKOBO!

255
00:21:14,328 --> 00:21:18,248
いいわねいいわね！次はゼータ！
Cool, cool! Zeta's turn, Zeta's turn!

256
00:21:18,383 --> 00:21:25,248
「ミッションスタート」って言ったら一緒に「スタート」って言うわ！
Okay, okay. When I say "Mission Starto", you all shout "Starto" together!

257
00:21:25,383 --> 00:21:27,690
いい？アアア！ミッション…
Ready? Ahh... mission...

258
00:21:27,772 --> 00:21:31,248
スタート！
Starto!

259
00:21:34,383 --> 00:21:35,690
次はカエラ！
Okay, Kaela's next!

260
00:21:35,837 --> 00:21:40,248
よしよし！きてみんもそしてholoh3roも
Alright! This is for all the fans and HoloH3ro too.

261
00:21:40,383 --> 00:21:45,801
「holoh3ro！」って言ったら「HU-HA！」で返してね！簡単でしょ？
When I say "HoloH3ro!", you respond with "HU-HA!". Easy, right?

262
00:21:45,941 --> 00:21:48,690
さあさあさあ！
Let's go, let's go!

263
00:21:48,772 --> 00:21:50,801
準備はいい？ holoh3ro！
Ready? HoloH3ro!

264
00:21:50,870 --> 00:21:54,272
HU-HA！
HU-HA!

265
00:21:54,870 --> 00:21:58,248
いいわねいいわね！
Great, great, great!

266
00:21:58,837 --> 00:22:03,690
いいわ、ついに3期生は息ぴったり
Awesome. Finally, Gen 3 is in sync.

267
00:22:03,837 --> 00:22:07,248
そうわ、まだまだ元気が残りそうね
Yeah, looks like everyone's still full of energy.

268
00:22:07,383 --> 00:22:11,701
だって、今日の一曲目だけどももうすごく伝わってくるんだもん
I mean, even from our first song today, I can really feel it.

269
00:22:11,837 --> 00:22:15,870
みんな、まさか私たちの1曲目が「100％」だったなんて思ってた？
Did you guys ever suspect that our first song would be "100%"?

270
00:22:15,941 --> 00:22:20,690
思うわけないよな、私もびっくりした
No way anyone did. Even I was surprised myself.

271
00:22:20,772 --> 00:22:25,870
ホシノヴァ気分でライブ開始だなんて！すごいよね？
Opening with Hoshinova mode like that. It was cool, right?

272
00:22:25,941 --> 00:22:30,870
かっこいいっすね、しかもさっきゼータとが歌った…いや違う
It was so cool. Especially earlier when Zeta sang... no, wait.

273
00:22:30,941 --> 00:22:36,248
ゼータとか？ゼータとカエラが歌った時はもう本家の「100％」みたいっす
Zeta? When Zeta and Kaela sang "100%", it felt like the real "100%".

274
00:22:36,328 --> 00:22:41,248
マジかっこよすぎなんだけど、なんか、うー！うー！ってなってき！
It was just way too cool, I was like, "Whoa! Whoa!"

275
00:22:41,837 --> 00:22:44,701
あんあなかっこいい歌を歌ったことあるのかな？
Have you guys ever sung such a cool song before?

276
00:22:44,772 --> 00:22:47,690
かっこつけてんの？本物のかっこつけ
Aura farming? Real aura farming right there.

277
00:22:47,772 --> 00:22:50,870
そう、かっこつけてる、だってムーナの曲がかっこいいもん
Yeah, it was cool. Moona's songs are just so cool.

278
00:22:50,941 --> 00:22:56,248
だってゼータがいつもスタイリッシュとかジャズっぽい曲ばっかっしょ？
Because Zeta usually does stylish or jazzy songs, right?

279
00:22:56,328 --> 00:23:01,690
だからさっき「100％」を歌った時めっちゃ雰囲気が違う
So when we sang "100%" just now, the vibes felt completely different.

280
00:23:01,772 --> 00:23:04,701
しかもカエラのラップも！
And Kaela's rap too!

281
00:23:04,837 --> 00:23:09,690
なんかこう…とにかくかっこよかった！すごいわ！
It was like... anyway, it was so cool! Amazing!

282
00:23:09,837 --> 00:23:14,272
とにかくかっこよかった！すごいわ！
Yeah, it was really cool, really cool earlier.

283
00:23:14,383 --> 00:23:19,248
でも、それだけじゃないよ！次の曲が「NEW ZOMBIE!!」でした！
But that's not all! The next song was "NEW ZOMBIE!!".

284
00:23:19,383 --> 00:23:21,701
これだれの曲かわかるよね？
I'm sure you all know whose song this is?

285
00:23:21,837 --> 00:23:25,801
もちろんたよ、うちの先輩だ
Of course, it's our senpai's.

286
00:23:25,941 --> 00:23:31,701
holoroのパフォーマンスもめっちゃかっこよかったよ、まるでゲームの中にいるみたいだった
Holoro's performance was also really cool, it felt like being inside a game.

287
00:23:31,837 --> 00:23:35,690
そうっわ！しかもバックダンサーもいたし
That's right! And there were backup dancers too, man.

288
00:23:35,837 --> 00:23:38,801
かっこよかったっすね！
It was so cool, guys! Right?!

289
00:23:39,383 --> 00:23:43,690
他になんかあったかな？レーザーも花火も…
What else was there? Laser lights and fireworks too.

290
00:23:43,837 --> 00:23:47,701
すごいギミックがたくさんあったっすね！
There were so many amazing stage gimmicks!

291
00:23:47,837 --> 00:23:50,690
あのバックダンサーたちあたしのソロライブに雇うっす
I'm going to hire all those backup dancers for my solo concert.

292
00:23:50,837 --> 00:23:53,248
おっと、もうソロライブの話？
Whoa, already talking about a solo concert.

293
00:23:53,383 --> 00:23:55,272
まあ言葉も祈りってやつ
Well, thoughts become prayers.

294
00:23:55,870 --> 00:24:03,248
でもこのライブはまだ終わらないよ！まだあど！
But this concert isn't over yet. Not yet, not yet.

295
00:24:03,837 --> 00:24:11,272
でも…さっき何の歌を歌ったか知ってる？
But... do you guys know what song was sung before this?

296
00:24:11,383 --> 00:24:16,248
もちろんたよ、私の新しい曲たから
Of course I know, it's my new song, "dahlah.".

297
00:24:16,837 --> 00:24:19,272
そうっすね、まあいいや
Yeah, forget it.

298
00:24:19,801 --> 00:24:22,248
まあいい
Forget it.

299
00:24:22,772 --> 00:24:27,690
いやいや！タイトルは「dahlah.」だよ！「dahlah.」！
No, wait! The title is "dahlah.". "dahlah."!

300
00:24:27,837 --> 00:24:31,701
おおなるほど
Oh, I see.

301
00:24:31,837 --> 00:24:36,701
「dahlah.」だったか…先に言ってよ！
So it was "dahlah."... You should've said so!

302
00:24:36,837 --> 00:24:42,690
だっていつもそれ言ってるじゃん、本当にまぁいいやって思ってた
You say it all the time, I thought you were just being casual.

303
00:24:42,837 --> 00:24:46,248
それ言って帰ると思ってた
I thought you were just saying it and going home.

